---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | ToolCompareLabs" description="ToolCompareLabs privacy policy and data handling practices.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-8 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: June 29, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-slate max-w-none">
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>ToolCompareLabs ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.</p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect minimal data to operate and improve our services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: We use analytics tools (e.g., Google Analytics, Plausible) to understand how visitors interact with our site. This includes IP address (anonymized), browser type, pages visited, and referral source.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: We use essential cookies for site functionality and optional analytics cookies. You can control cookie preferences through your browser settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Affiliate Tracking</strong>: When you click on affiliate links, the respective platform (e.g., Impact) may set tracking cookies to attribute referrals. This is governed by the third-party platform's privacy policy.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To analyze website traffic and improve content quality</li>
        <li>To track affiliate link performance and calculate commissions</li>
        <li>To ensure website security and prevent abuse</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong>: CDN and security services</li>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong>: Traffic analysis (with IP anonymization enabled)</li>
        <li><strong>Impact</strong>: Affiliate tracking and commission management</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Analytics data is retained for 26 months maximum. We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information.</p>

      <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Under GDPR and applicable privacy laws, you have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at privacy@toolcomparelabs.com.</p>

      <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
